Question: In CircuiTikZ, you want to combine a perpendicular drawing with a wire ending shape. Which of the following code snippets would correctly achieve this effect?

A) \draw (A) to[short,*-,|-] ($(A)!0.5!(sel.lpin 4)$) -| (sel.lpin 4);

